        "description": "\ud83d\ude9a FREE DELIVERY in the East Village! \ud83d\udc99\n\nGetting your medications just got easier.\nNo travel. No waiting. No extra cost.\n\n\ud83d\udce6 Prescription & OTC delivery \u2014 straight to your door\n\ud83d\udc75 Perfect for seniors, busy families & anyone who values convenience\n\u23f1\ufe0f Fast \u2022 Reliable \u2022 Local care you can trust\n\n\ud83d\udccd Serving East Village residents\n\ud83d\udcde Call or message us today to set up FREE delivery\n\nBecause your health should come with convenience \u2728#instatrip #freedelivery #eastvillage #eastvillageresident #delivery #prescription #convenience #care #residents #values",
        "date": "Jan 20, 2026"
      },
      {
        "media": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc/AF1QipM0YaiTWTQZ8UA8Fpd65cElKuPhFKnTnLXj8AgZ=h400-no",
