        "description": "\ud83d\udc8a Medication Made Simple in New York City \ud83d\udc99\n\nManaging multiple medications doesn\u2019t have to be confusing.\nAt New York City Pharmacy, our Unit Dose Pouch Packaging is designed with older adults in mind.\n\n\u2705 Easy-to-open pouches\n\u2705 Clearly labeled by date & time\n\u2705 No pill bottles, no pill sorting\n\u2705 Fewer missed doses, more peace of mind\n\nWhether at home or on the go, pouch packaging helps seniors stay safe, independent, and confident with their medications.\n\n\ud83d\udccd Ask us today how pouch packaging can make daily medications easier for you or your loved ones.\n\n#MedicationMadeEasy #SeniorCare #PouchPackaging #UnitDose #NYCPharmacy #HealthyAging",
        "date": "Jan 17, 2026"
      },
      {
        "media": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc/AF1QipNBMHnzrXrxCnFrbu1nsX88bsph1rdyB8seMRvX=h400-no",
