        "description": "NYC pet parents\u2014good news! **New York City Pharmacy** now carries **pet medications** for your furry family\u2014**cats & dogs** (OTC + prescriptions).  \nShop online: **http://www.nycprx.com**        \n\nHave questions or need help finding the right product? Message us or call\u2014we\u2019re happy to help you get what your pet needs.\n\n*Prescription medications require a valid prescription from your veterinarian.*\n\n#NYCPets #PetMedications #CatsOfNYC #DogsOfNYC #NYCPharmacy #PetCare\n\n#furryfamily #otc #petparent #newyork #petmedications #familycats #pharmacy #petcare",
        "date": "Jan 15, 2026"
      },
