          "description": "I cannot speak highly enough about this pharmacy team. Chintan and Lokesh are not only excellent pharmacists, they are genuinely kind and compassionate people. They embody what it means to be true neighborhood pharmacists.\n\nI still remember when Chintan kindly notarized an adoption paper for me and, with a smile, wished me luck and refused to charge a fee. That simple gesture of generosity spoke volumes about his character.\n\nLokesh, too, is one of the sweetest and most caring individuals you will meet. He consistently goes out of his way to find the best possible deals on medications, always putting patients first.\n\nThis is a pharmacy you can trust with both your health and your heart. I wholeheartedly recommend them as your go-to pharmacists. Support local, especially when it\u2019s a team that serves the community with such compassion and professionalism.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pOSU9HVTBTMU5QYlhSVldIWnNUMGd3U21vM1owRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x9547198182810a70!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOjNIOGU0S1NPbXRVWHZsT0gwSmo3Z0E%7C%7C?hl=en",
